project_descr: After a study conducted in 2015 about Joint Presence Offices (JPOs) in the Pacific. The UN system agreed to establish JPOs in the Cook Island & Niue to be led by UN Coordination  Officers for 3 years (2016-2018).

outputs.output_descr: United Nations agreed to establish a Joint Presence Offices and placing UN Coordination officer in the Cook Islands, this will contribute to the UN development system leadership and coordination.
